content.raw:
Should we add `LD_LIBRARY_PATH`  to `GAZEBO_PLUGIN_PATH`? ie

~~~
GAZEBO_PLUGIN_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH IGN_GUI_PLUGIN_PATH=src/gui gazebo
~~~

otherwise I get the following msg when running this cmd probably due to recently merged pull request #26. 

~~~
Err] [gazebo_main.cc:117] Failed to load library gazeboPhysicsSystem
~~~
content.html:
Should we add LD_LIBRARY_PATH to GAZEBO_PLUGIN_PATH? ie

GAZEBO_PLUGIN_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH IGN_GUI_PLUGIN_PATH=src/gui gazebo

otherwise I get the following msg when running this cmd probably due to recently merged pull request #26. 

Err] [gazebo_main.cc:117] Failed to load library gazeboPhysicsSystem
